Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.70,0:02:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}正如書面上所寫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.80,0:02:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要把我革職
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.00,0:02:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.20,0:02:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.70,0:02:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳明不明白都好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.30,0:02:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是董事會的決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.10,0:02:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若不服氣 妳就遞交辭呈好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.70,0:02:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣 媽媽會比較高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.70,0:02:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可以...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.00,0:02:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟為甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.80,0:02:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理由也不用多說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.50,0:02:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說車隊的成績不振
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.80,0:02:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.90,0:02:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 前天的董事會裡從未議論那件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.70,0:02:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這一季的展開也沒有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.60,0:03:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有更好的方法的話 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.10,0:03:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家當然會去做別的選擇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.40,0:03:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳也會那樣做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.20,0:03:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你意思是說有比把我革職更好的方法?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.30,0:03:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國內汽車市場佔有率堪稱第一\N的葵企業在閃電霹靂車為何贏不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.60,0:03:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被別人那樣說 妳會怎樣想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.70,0:03:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.70,0:03:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以來我給過妳足夠的機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.40,0:03:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是抽身的時候了 今日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.30,0:03:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也不應該在這時候...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.50,0:03:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離開幕不足一個月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.30,0:03:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當然知道沒有時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.90,0:03:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 「他」肯定地說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.40,0:03:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今季一定會贏取冠軍給我們看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.40,0:03:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.40,0:03:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名雲京志郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.50,0:03:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位在我們面前保證今季會奪冠的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.40,0:03:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是你的繼任人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.20,0:04:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起了 要你久等 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.20,0:04:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.80,0:04:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揭幕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.30,0:04:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,華麗的舞台就在眼前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.80,0:04:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆被降職為副社長?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.60,0:04:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.60,0:04:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到會有這樣和妳一起共事的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.90,0:04:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運的女神好像終於也注意我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.70,0:04:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是葵今日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.50,0:04:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.00,0:04:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.90,0:04:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我是第一次和妳見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.30,0:04:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但妳的事我很早就有所耳聞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.80,0:04:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無意間失禮了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.30,0:04:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳變得很美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.90,0:05:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 我佩服妳能努力到這地步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.90,0:05:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過獎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.80,0:05:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你現在這樣說讓我聽來覺得是在諷刺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.60,0:05:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請妳別那樣說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.10,0:05:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也從祖父和爸爸那裡聽過許多關於你的傳聞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.70,0:05:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你是最具才幹最平步青雲的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.80,0:05:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為目前為止我老是碰巧遇上好做的工作而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.20,0:05:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我真正的未來現在才要開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.40,0:05:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.40,0:05:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道現在閃電霹靂車的形勢很嚴峻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.50,0:05:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我是第一次率領車隊去比賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.10,0:05:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間不多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.50,0:05:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有很多事一定要請妳協助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.70,0:05:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你敢保證會奪冠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.90,0:05:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但說話卻很小心呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.70,0:05:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會奪冠的 絕對會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.90,0:05:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是為了妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.30,0:06:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳會認為我明明是門外漢卻在大言不慚是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.80,0:06:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果沒有這樣的氣勢怎麼能在勝負的世界裡爭雄？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.20,0:06:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為結果就是一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.60,0:06:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有努力是一點意義都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.80,0:06:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問今天要去試車場嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.70,0:06:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 下午去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.70,0:06:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新跑車已進入最終調整階段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.50,0:06:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使社長換了人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.20,0:06:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照樣還是得為開幕做準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.30,0:06:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我也和跟妳去試車場吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.90,0:06:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時我想我能讓妳看懂我的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.43,0:06:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0}富士岡賽車場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.60,0:06:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C零件還有幾個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.50,0:06:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩套 要用嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.60,0:06:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成的新X六輪GT 超乎預料的好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.10,0:07:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今季絕對不會落後修特洛普拉姆斯和菅生車隊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.70,0:07:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然還要有人別下太荒唐的指示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.60,0:07:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請妳別那樣刁難我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.20,0:07:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 你不是說你有你的想法嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.00,0:07:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 我想妳很快就會知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.30,0:07:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.10,0:07:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.70,0:07:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.80,0:07:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼有個奇怪的傢伙闖進車道來？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.80,0:07:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣?有嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.90,0:08:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 今日的預定表裡沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.90,0:08:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.60,0:08:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道那是你的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.50,0:08:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 來個小比賽怎樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.60,0:08:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 賽三圈怎樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.10,0:08:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在想什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.20,0:08:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然讓訓練安排裡沒有的車子進入車道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.90,0:08:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太危險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.50,0:08:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會有危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.90,0:08:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他們全是職業車手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.50,0:08:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.70,0:08:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳自豪的新X六輪GT不是已經在最終調整了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.20,0:08:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說 你害怕它會輸嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.30,0:08:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的!?時速七百公里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.70,0:08:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們聽好了 下次經過終點線後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.80,0:08:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑三圈跟車子決一勝負
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.10,0:08:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 妳突然間講甚麼呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.60,0:08:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這又沒有在預定中...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.70,0:08:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用多說 快比
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.00,0:08:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸了的話 我不會輕饒你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.30,0:09:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我現在正在測試啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.60,0:09:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不能...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.60,0:09:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用再囉嗦了 這樣才能看出有沒有調整好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.50,0:09:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們要當作真正的比賽去跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.50,0:09:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.80,0:09:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰來記錄一下時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.00,0:09:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管了 既然她都那麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.90,0:09:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管它是哪來的賽車 我才不會輸呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.70,0:09:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才妳看見了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.30,0:09:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像做了奇怪的變形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.00,0:09:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.70,0:09:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?差距愈來愈大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.50,0:09:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了!我已經馬力全開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.10,0:10:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.10,0:10:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1分11秒554
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.60,0:10:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比加賀的圈速記錄快了兩秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.60,0:10:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子不用三圈就決出勝負了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.70,0:10:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想說甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.60,0:10:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何有這樣...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.20,0:10:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是說妳的想法還太天真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.00,0:10:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能夠獲勝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.60,0:10:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新X六輪GT開發就到今天為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.60,0:10:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不想在冠軍杯上也遇到同樣的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.20,0:10:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.60,0:10:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為再跑下去也是白跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.90,0:10:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白白弄壞車子而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.00,0:10:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個速度跟我們的級別不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.80,0:10:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有勝算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.60,0:10:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.40,0:10:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那輛車子在這車道跑出的最好時間是1分10秒462
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.80,0:10:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 那輛車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.20,0:10:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不會因為操作錯誤而發生意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.80,0:10:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新條
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.30,0:11:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎內壓上升 再奔跑會有危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.80,0:11:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請停車吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.70,0:11:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會一直受人欺壓的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.60,0:11:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新條
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.70,0:11:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新條 車壞了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.20,0:11:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然車壞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.40,0:11:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但沒關係了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.60,0:11:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不會使用那車子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.80,0:11:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.20,0:11:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了 菲爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.60,0:11:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 剛來就驚嚇了大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.50,0:11:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我想還是早點讓你們看到的好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.80,0:12:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車名是 葵．AL-ZARD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.40,0:12:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是葵車隊的跑車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.70,0:12:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不是工廠裡製造出來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.60,0:12:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那究竟是在哪裡造出這部車的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.40,0:12:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成這部車的 是我的企劃組
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.80,0:12:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它所搭載的是生化電腦 AL-ZARD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.40,0:12:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車身使用了稀有金屬T3000
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.10,0:12:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生化電腦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.20,0:12:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼稀有金屬？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.90,0:12:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 果然...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.50,0:12:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看見了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.00,0:12:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的變形方式是過去所沒有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.60,0:12:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點也沒有浪費
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.10,0:12:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,融合這兩種最尖端科技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.30,0:12:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我的企劃的主題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.40,0:12:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我本來沒打算用來製造閃電霹靂車的跑車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.30,0:12:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我接到社長的提議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.40,0:12:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說它最適合用在閃電霹靂車裡的系統上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.00,0:13:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是 誕生了這部 AL-ZARD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.80,0:13:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.10,0:13:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從未跟我提起這件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.20,0:13:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為當時還不知道會有什麼結果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.40,0:13:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有了它 我們就能報一箭之仇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.60,0:13:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還擊修特洛普拉姆斯和菅生也是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.80,0:13:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今季我會用這部AL-ZARD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.40,0:13:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿下冠軍杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.60,0:13:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有異議吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.70,0:13:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.60,0:13:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他從開發階段起就一直駕駛AL-ZARD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.80,0:13:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他叫菲爾．弗利茲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.70,0:13:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒有參加大賽的經驗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.30,0:13:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他是個很讓人期待的新人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.60,0:13:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新條
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.00,0:13:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新條!沒事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.00,0:13:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新條
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.70,0:13:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 老闆 我把新車...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.50,0:13:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.50,0:13:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 你不必在意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.40,0:13:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們不會用那輛車了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.90,0:13:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你被解雇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.90,0:13:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.70,0:14:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.20,0:14:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾 我的車隊不需要他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.40,0:14:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你胡說些甚麼傻話 在這時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.00,0:14:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在任何時候 不需要的東西就是不需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.50,0:14:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會派菲爾和加賀參加冠軍杯賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.00,0:14:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們才值得期待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.80,0:14:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.30,0:14:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然想解雇經驗豐富的新條
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.10,0:14:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而起用一個什麼都不懂的新人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.80,0:14:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事我不同意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.60,0:14:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賽車不是經驗豐富的人就能贏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.70,0:14:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是他這種情況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.70,0:14:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.00,0:14:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是假設
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.10,0:14:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你這是對有拿過冠軍的賽車手說的話嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.90,0:14:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說冠軍？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.20,0:14:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那一年是沒有什麼人參賽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.20,0:14:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳認為那種冠軍誰會認同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.70,0:14:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能說是暫時的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.00,0:14:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他在心理方面有太多的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.50,0:14:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一激動起來就失去作為車手的冷靜判斷力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.90,0:14:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛不也是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.60,0:15:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加賀看出極限來而減低車速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.20,0:15:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他卻意氣用事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.40,0:15:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是這樣才演出終點前用光汽油的醜態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.40,0:15:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加賀雖然沒有冠軍頭銜 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.70,0:15:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但誰都認同實力方面是加賀略勝一籌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.90,0:15:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前年和那個奇跡的世界冠軍\N風見隼人演出一幕驚人決鬥的也是加賀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.80,0:15:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說再用這個人有什麼意義？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.40,0:15:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.50,0:15:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副社長!請妳適可而止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.40,0:15:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這樣庇護他、寵他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.30,0:15:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果等於害了自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.00,0:15:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不忍心解雇贏不了比賽車手的老闆是個問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.80,0:15:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但贏不了比賽的車手問題更大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.90,0:15:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之今天上演的開除戲就是這道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.90,0:15:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你別胡說好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.90,0:15:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這與那是兩回事...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.30,0:15:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白妳寵愛自己培養的賽車手的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.80,0:16:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 對那種抱著天塌下來也有人擋著的心態的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.20,0:16:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待他有好結果是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.00,0:16:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而妳這樣寵溺他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.70,0:16:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會使他更加無能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.50,0:16:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新條
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.80,0:16:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新條
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.40,0:16:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過分!你在胡說甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.10,0:16:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許我說得的確殘酷了點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.20,0:16:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是把話挑明講對彼此都有益
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.00,0:16:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新條…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.20,0:16:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳看著吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.40,0:16:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會把勝利的榮耀獻給妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.10,0:16:43.90,Sonjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}迷路の出口どこなのか
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.90,0:16:47.60,Sonjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}誰も知らずに走ってる
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.60,0:16:54.80,Sonjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}ほんとうはすぐそこにあっても气がつかずに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.10,0:16:58.50,Sonjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}梦破れてもはぐれてもやり直せるよ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.90,0:16:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏不了比賽的車手問題更大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.20,0:16:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.90,0:17:06.20,Sonjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}何もかも振り出しまで唳ったとしても
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.20,0:17:09.60,Sonjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}あなたの輝き
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.90,0:17:12.00,Sonjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}強くなる度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.00,0:17:15.80,Sonjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}私のこと變えてゆく
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.80,0:17:21.10,Sonjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}倒れそうなとき 思い出してね
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.10,0:17:28.70,Sonjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}あなたは今ひとりきりじゃないこと Believe！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.90,0:17:36.40,Sonjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}行き止まりも遠回りも厭わずに行くのが
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.40,0:17:39.90,Sonjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}そばにいても離れててもどこにいてもずっと
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.90,0:17:48.80,Sonjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\fad(000,1000)}あなたのこと思っている私がいるからいつも感じてて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.50,0:17:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加賀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.10,0:18:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新條!你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.20,0:18:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你振作過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.90,0:18:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有點憔悴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.50,0:18:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心情的影響多少有點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.60,0:18:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是作為車手現在才是開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.80,0:18:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 我想問你一些事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.40,0:18:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想問別人的意見 禮物就只是那些嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.10,0:18:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早料到你會那樣說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.30,0:18:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想聽我的意見對吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.30,0:18:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是要用到這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.80,0:18:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美國?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.30,0:18:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我想試著去突破過去到現在的瓶頸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.30,0:18:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去那個賽車之國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.00,0:18:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參加卡車大賽或是普通型賽車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.10,0:18:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 我想拚命參加各種不同的比賽磨練自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.00,0:18:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為新社長的話也有道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.80,0:19:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的確是很天真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.50,0:19:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對車隊是 對老闆也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.40,0:19:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.40,0:19:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是什麼常敗的車手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.90,0:19:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我是說我一點也沒有那個意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.40,0:19:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我缺乏某種東西確實是事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.80,0:19:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要去美國把它找出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.30,0:19:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我考慮許久得出的結論
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.60,0:19:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這倒是不錯呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.90,0:19:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以你這個模範生來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.60,0:19:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為那是好主意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.70,0:19:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去過那裡後應該會變得更大膽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.30,0:19:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.30,0:19:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟美貴說了沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.50,0:19:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 我現在沒臉見她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.40,0:19:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我老在她面前出醜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.60,0:19:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.10,0:19:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那邊安定下來後我會和她聯繫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.40,0:20:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡玩賽車的情況是怎樣的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.50,0:20:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新條
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.00,0:20:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我在那邊朋友的地址
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.80,0:20:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有甚麼事就試著去找他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.70,0:20:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們看起來很凶險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.10,0:20:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但全是很講義氣的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.20,0:20:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.85,0:20:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0}美國 曼哈頓島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.10,0:20:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城之內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.10,0:21:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 還人這樣為你擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.70,0:21:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然不先找我就走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.10,0:21:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.10,0:21:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城之內...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.20,0:21:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,44號登機口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.90,0:21:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.30,0:21:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了做你的技師來葵車隊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.00,0:21:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有你 我留在那裡有什麼意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.40,0:21:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想去美國玩賽車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.90,0:21:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就替你去維修車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.10,0:21:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這樣決定的 就這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.80,0:21:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城之內...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.00,0:21:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 情況不是任何時候都那麼樂觀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.00,0:21:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年對我來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.40,0:21:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在某方面來講情況也可以說是嚴峻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.30,0:22:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我對花環沒有任何顧忌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.70,0:22:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是一部擁有優秀性能的車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.30,0:22:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也使用它相當一段日子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.40,0:22:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不只比賽整體的方向性在逐漸改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.20,0:22:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連車子也一樣在變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.70,0:22:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那種形勢裡能發揮怎樣的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.10,0:22:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我所在意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.90,0:22:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你接受採訪 祝你好運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.10,0:22:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.70,0:22:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風見先生還是那麼酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.60,0:22:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 這一季我要好好加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.20,0:22:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳還在說呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.90,0:22:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.70,0:22:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香小姐不在 現在是大好機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.40,0:22:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用這鍛煉出來的好身材
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.90,0:22:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把風見先生迷死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.80,0:22:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年也聽過你相同的台詞呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.20,0:22:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.70,0:22:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳那胸圍跟明日香比起來還早得很呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.50,0:22:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳甚麼意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.70,0:22:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 菅生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.80,0:22:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.40,0:22:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不...我還不習慣 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.60,0:22:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的新臉孔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.70,0:23:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說新臉孔真是失禮呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.30,0:23:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要說變回原來的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.80,0:23:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 我來介紹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.80,0:23:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的新人 雷歐．安哈特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.10,0:23:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.90,0:23:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.20,0:23:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算甚麼問候啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.80,0:23:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要更有禮貌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.90,0:23:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是菅生修
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.30,0:23:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是...雷歐．安哈特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.70,0:23:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 雷歐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.90,0:23:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你終於當教官了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.90,0:23:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也難怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.60,0:23:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的年紀是最大的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.40,0:23:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我還不至於會輸給這些菜鳥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.40,0:23:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這小子年紀和風見一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.80,0:23:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻輕浮得要命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.00,0:23:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這跟賽車完全沒有關係啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.90,0:23:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看似沒有其實有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.30,0:23:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 這小子和葵車隊的新人是同期的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.40,0:23:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那斯卡時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.20,0:23:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於要到了新人的時代了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.70,0:23:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別擋住晚輩的路哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.10,0:23:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡說八道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.20,0:24:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葵的新人 菲爾．弗利茲嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.70,0:24:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預賽開始經過30分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.10,0:24:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頂尖車隊陸續在向極速挑戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.00,0:24:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫定的最優先起跑位置是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.40,0:24:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛開始就跑出1分37秒266
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.70,0:24:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修特洛普拉姆斯的合作夥伴傑奇．古德利安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.10,0:24:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有誰能突破這個紀錄呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:25.60,0:24:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風見隼人現在通過控制線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:32.70,0:24:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害 厲害
