Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:31.50,0:25:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新條竟然不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:33.30,0:25:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得有點難以相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:36.60,0:25:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位新車手在昨日的自由試車裡
